---
import ServiceDetailLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayoutDetails.astro";
import { SERVICES } from "../../utils/constants";

const babyService = SERVICES.find((service) => service.slug === "baby-shoot");

// Additional metadata specifically for Baby Shoot service
const serviceMetadata = {
  metaDescription:
    "Capture your baby's special moments with professional baby photography in Nagpur. Adorable props, gentle lighting, and a baby-friendly studio at Pixxel City.",
  ogImage: "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/retro-studio-baby_shoot.jpg",
  canonicalUrl: "https://pixxelcity.com/services/baby-shoot",
  keywords:
    "baby photoshoot nagpur, newborn photography, baby portfolio shoot, child photo studio, baby-friendly photography studio",
};

// Enhance the service object with additional metadata
const enhancedService = {
  ...babyService,
  ...serviceMetadata,
  heroImage: "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/retro-studio-baby_shoot.jpg",
  process: [
    {
      title: "Pre-Shoot Planning",
      description:
        "We consult with you to understand your baby's comfort needs, preferred themes, and the best timing for the shoot.",
    },
    {
      title: "Setup & Prop Preparation",
      description:
        "Our team prepares safe, adorable sets with sanitized props and calming lights to keep your baby relaxed.",
    },
    {
      title: "Gentle Photography Session",
      description:
        "The session is paced according to your baby’s mood and needs, with breaks for feeding, naps, or cuddles.",
    },
    {
      title: "Family & Sibling Shots",
      description:
        "We also capture beautiful moments with parents and siblings, creating a complete memory collection.",
    },
    {
      title: "Final Selection & Delivery",
      description:
        "You’ll receive a curated gallery of professionally edited photos, perfect for keepsakes, prints, or digital sharing.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<ServiceDetailLayout service={enhancedService}>
  <Fragment slot="service-content">
    <h3>Capture Your Baby’s Precious Moments</h3>

    <p>
      A baby photoshoot is more than just pictures—it’s a timeless memory of
      your little one’s earliest days. At Pixxel City Studio, we offer a
      baby-friendly environment designed to capture genuine smiles, curious
      looks, and cuddly moments in a safe, gentle setting.
    </p>

    <p>
      From newborn sessions to toddler milestones, our team specializes in
      creating beautiful visuals that you’ll cherish for a lifetime. Every shoot
      is customized for your baby’s comfort and your family’s preferences.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <img
        src="https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/retro-studio-baby_shoot.jpg"
        alt="Adorable baby photoshoot with props"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1648376/pexels-photo-1648376.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
        alt="Newborn photography setup"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h3>Our Baby-Friendly Studio Experience</h3>

    <h4>Comfort First</h4>

    <p>
      Our studio is temperature-controlled and sanitized, with soft lighting and
      soothing music to keep your baby comfortable. We follow a baby-first
      approach, taking breaks whenever needed.
    </p>

    <h4>Themed Setups & Props</h4>

    <p>
      Choose from a variety of charming themes—from dreamy clouds to playful
      toys. We provide all props and backdrops, ensuring every frame looks
      perfect and adorable.
    </p>

    <h4>Safety is Our Priority</h4>

    <p>
      We use baby-safe materials, trained staff, and non-intrusive techniques.
      Whether your baby is a newborn or a curious toddler, our team ensures
      they’re in good hands throughout the session.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg my-8 border-l-4 border-primary"
    >
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        "Pixxel City Studio made our baby’s first photoshoot a joy. The team was
        incredibly patient, and the photos came out better than we could have
        imagined. Highly recommended for new parents!"
      </p>
      <cite class="block mt-4 font-medium">— A happy mom from Nagpur</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Perfect for Milestones & Memories</h3>

    <h4>Newborn Sessions (0–3 Months)</h4>

    <p>
      Capture those sleepy poses and tiny details in a peaceful setting that
      respects your baby’s rhythm and safety needs.
    </p>

    <h4>Half-Year Celebrations (6 Months)</h4>

    <p>
      Document your baby’s growing personality with playful, colorful themes
      that show off their budding curiosity and charm.
    </p>

    <h4>First Birthday Shoots (12 Months)</h4>

    <p>
      Celebrate your baby’s first year with a joyful shoot—complete with
      cakesmash, balloons, and themed decorations for unforgettable birthday
      memories.
    </p>

    <h3>Booking & Packages</h3>

    <p>
      Baby shoot sessions are typically 3–4 hours to allow time for feeding,
      breaks, and setup. Packages include multiple themes, family photos, and
      edited images. You’re welcome to bring your own outfit choices or favorite
      toys.
    </p>

    <p>
      To ensure a smooth session, we recommend pre-booking and sharing your
      preferences in advance. Our team will guide you through every step—from
      planning to delivery.
    </p>

    <h3>Let’s Create Memories Together</h3>

    <p>
      Book your baby’s photoshoot today and preserve these fleeting moments
      forever. Reach out to us for package details and date availability.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceDetailLayout>
